description: I started the hunt in front of a supermarket somewhere at the outskirts of Prague. Not the best idea as I noticed after a while. It took me more than half an hour to find a suitable guy for my game. He moved to Prague just recently. Living together with  some roommates he tries to start a new life. Right now he is working as a bartender. His salary including tips wasn´t so bad according to what he said. Still I was a bit skeptical as the amount appeared to me to be a bit too high. And as I was able to have a look at his shopping: just water and vegetables. Obviously he was quite broke this month so my offer for showing me his dick came quite handy. He did it right in front of the market. But would he also suck my dick? And then there was still this cucumber :-)
title: Czech Hunter 210
